<div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-3">
                <div class="profile-sidebar">
                    <img class="profile-user-pic" src="/images/products/A004.png" alt="product preview">

                        <div class="profile-user-name">
                            IPhone X - 256 GB
                        </div>


                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="profile-tabs tab-content col-md-9">
                <div id="overview" class="tab-pane fade show active">
                    <div class="card fav-card">
                         <div class="card-header bg-dark text-light">Add Product</div>
                        <div class="card-body">

                            <form class="form-horizontal" method="post" action="/admin/add_product/validate">
                             
                                <div class="form-group">
                                        <a> Name </a>
                                        <input  id="name" type="text" class="form-control" name="name" value="IPhone X - 256 GB" required autofocus>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="form-row">
                                           <div class="form-group col-md-6 ">
                                               <a> Brand </a>
                                               <input  id="brand" type="text" class="form-control" name="brand" value="B001" required>
                                           </div>
                                           <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                                               <a> Category </a>
                                               <input  id="category" type="text" class="form-control" name="category" value="F001" required>
                                           </div>
                                          </div>

                                    <div class="form-row">
                                        <div class="form-group col-md-6 ">
                                            <a> Warehouse </a>
                                            <input  id="price" type="text" class="form-control" name="price" value="A1" required>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="form-group col-md-6">
                                            <a> Score </a>
                                            <input  id="stock" type="text" class="form-control" name="score" value="4" required>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>

                                    <div class="form-group">
                                        <a> Description </a>
                                        <textarea id="description" type="text" class="form-control" name="description" rows="10"required>smartphone com capacidade de armazenamento de 256 GB e ecrã Super Retina de 5,8” (2436 x 1125 píxeis a 458 ppp), com relação de contraste de 1000000:1; resistente à água e ao pó; Face ID; processador A11 Bionic com arquitetura de 64 bits; carregamento sem fios; câmaras grande angular e teleobjetiva de 12 MP e câmara TrueDepth; gravação vídeo 4K a 24, 30 ou 60 fps; autonomia em conversação (sem fios) de até 21 horas.</textarea>
                                    </div>

                                    <div  class="form-group">
                                        <a> Product Image </a>
                                        <input style="margin-left:20px;"type="file" name="avatar">
                                    </div>


                                    <div class="form-group float-right">
                                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-dark ">Next</button>
                                    </div>

                                </form>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>